---
title: Mushroom & Bacon Fettuccine Boscaiola with Rocket & Pear Salad
description: This fettuccine dish pairs the earthy flavours of mushrooms with an easy creamy sauce. The side salad balances the richness of
the pasta with a sweet and juicy pear.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6698b8174b756a3c9819067b-452cf42c.jpeg
